quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  52,24,Kuya kuhamba hamba phakathi kwabo (izicaka) ezingamakhwenkwana azele ukulungiselela bona engathi ziiperile ezilondoloziweyo
  52,25,Ke kaloku baya kusondelana babuzane
  52,26,"Baya kuthi: “Inene thina kwixesha elidlulileyo esasikunye nabantu bakuthi ngalo sasisoyika (ukumenza umsindo uAllâh)"
  52,27,"Waza uAllâh Wasibonelela ngobuBele baKhe, Wasikhusela kananjalo kwisohlwayo soMlilo otshisayo"
  52,28,"Inene sasidla ngokucela kuYe ngaphambili. Inene, nguYe OnguMncedi, uSozinceba"
  52,29,Ngoko ke wena (Muhammad) khumbuza kuba wena ngoBabalo lweNkosi yakho akungosiyavumisa okanye umntu ophambeneyo
  52,30,"Okanye bathi (ngawe): “Yimbongi esilindele ukuba ihlelwe lilishwa lexesha”"
  52,31,"Yithi wena: “Lindani kaloku, kuba nam phakathi kwenu ndingomnye wabalindileyo!”"
  52,32,"Makube mhlawumbi ziingqondo zabo ezibayalela ukuba (batsho) obu (buxoki ngawe Muhammad), okanye (bona) bangabantu nje abagabadeleyo"
  52,33,"Okanye bathi: “Uyiqambe ngokwakhe (i’Kur’ân)”? Yeha bona abakholwa"
  52,34,Mabavelise isicengcelezo esifana nayo (i’Kur’ân) kaloku ukuba bathetha inyaniso
  52,35,Makube mhlawumbi badalwa ngento engekhoyo? Okanye ngabo abangabadali
  52,36,Makube mhlawumbi ngabo abadala amazulu nomhlaba? Nakanye abaqinisekanga
  52,37,"Makube mhlawumbi banoovimba (bobutyebi) beNkosi yakho, Okanye bangabalawuli babo (oovimba abo)"
  52,38,"Okanye banomchankcatho (wokuya ezulwini) abaphulaphula ngawo (iimfihlelo zezulu)? Ukuba kunnalo, umphulaphuli lowo wabo makaze nobungqina obucacileyo kaloku"
  52,39,Okanye Yena (uAllâh) Uneentombi nibe nina ninoonyana
  52,40,"Okanye wena (Muhammad), ubabiza intlawulo (ngalo myalezo) ukuze bazive besindekile ngumthwalo (wetyala lentlawulo)"
  52,41,"Okanye banolwazi lokungabonwayo, abalubhala phantsi"
  52,42,Okanye baqulunqa icebo? Kodwa abo bangakholwayo ngabo ekuqulunqwa ngabo
  52,43,OkanyebanomnyeuthixoongaphandlekoAllâh?Makazukiswe uAllâh Ongentla kwayo yonke into abayayamanisa naYe
  52,44,"Ke kaloku xa benokubona iceba lisiwa livela esibhakabhakeni bangathi: “Ngamafu (njee) ayinqumba!”"
  52,45,Bayeke ke wena bade badibane neMini yabo abaya kubethwa bengaqondi
  52,46,"Mini leyo icebo labo lingayi kubanceda nto, bengayi kuncedwa nakuncedwa"
  52,47,Inene kwabo benze ubugwenxa sisohlwayo esingaphambili kunoku kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi
  52,48,"Ke kaloku wena (Muhammad) yiba nomonde ngesigqibo senkosi yakho kuba inene wena usemehlweni eThu, kananjalo zukisa (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi, yakho xa uvuka"
  52,49,Nangenxalenye yobusuku Mzukise Yena nasemva (kokutshona) kweenkwenkwezi
  53,1,(Ndifunga) ngenkwenkwezi xa isihla
  53,2,Ugxa wenu (uMuhammad) akalahlekanga yaye akenzanga mpazamo
  53,3,Engathethi okomnqweno wakhe
  53,4,Asinto yimbi (le ‘Kur’ân) ngaphandle kokuba sisiTyhilelo esityhiliweyo
  53,5,Ufundiswe ngonamandla amakhulu (uJibrîl)
  53,6,"Ongenasiphene, yena waphakama waba ngemo yakhe yokwenene"
  53,7,Lo gama waye kwindawo ephakamileyo yolundi
  53,8,"Weza, wehla phantsi"
  53,9,Waba kumgama ongangobude bezaphetha ezibini okanye nganeno (kunoko)
  53,10,Watyhila (uJibrîl) kwisicaka saKhe (uAllâh) awakutyhilayo
  53,11,Intliziyo (ingqondo) ayizanga ixoke ngoko yakubonayo
  53,12,Niza kumphikisa na nina ngoko wakubonayo
  53,13,"Kananjalo\twambona\tyena\t(uMuhammad)\tngenene kwisihlandlo sesibini"
  53,14,NgakwiSidratul Muntaha
  53,15,"Kufutshane\tnayo\t(iSidratul\tMuntaha)\tkukho\tumyezo wokhuseleko (iPaladesi)"
  53,16,Yabona wathi usakugqunywa uMthi womLote yiloo nto yayiwugqumile
  53,17,Amehlo (OMprofeti uMuhammad) akalaqaza (ajonge kwenye indawo) engazanga agabadele
  53,18,Yena (wayibona ngenene eyona miqondiso mikhulu yeNkosi yakhe)
  53,19,Ke (nina) nibajongile na ooAl- Lat- noAl ‘Uzzâ
  53,20,"NoManât, ongowesithathu kubo"
  53,21,Ingaba okwenu ngabesiduna na ize kuYe ibe ngabesikhomokazi
  53,22,Oko ke (ukuba kunjalo) kukwaba okungenabulungisa
  53,23,"(Lawo) akanto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba ngamagama (njee) eniziqambele ngokwenu nina kunye nookhokho benu (magama lawo) uAllâh Angathumelanga gunya (ngawo) Abalandeli nto ngaphandle koqash-qash noko kunqwenelwa yimiphefumlo yabo, ukanti sele sifikile kubo isiKhokelo esivela eNkosini yabo"
  53,24,Ingaba umntu unako (konke) akunqwenelayo
  53,25,Kodwa uBomi belizayo bobuka-Allah nobokuqala